Season 1, Episode 26: Hack Prine
Original Air Date: 12 May 1956
Far from Dodge and without a horse Matt Dillon still manages to bring in Lee Trimble...a man wanted for murder. Lee&#039;s brother Dolph swears that he&#039;ll get him out.
